Feature: (Jelly-Fingers Curse)

    Causes the target's fingers to become almost jelly-like to make it
    impossible for the victim to grasp objects. If the opponent touches a wall,
    he/she will be stuck to it forever.

    Pronunciation: - 
    Seen/mentioned:
        After a June 1999 Portree/Arrows Quidditch game, the losing Seeker
        accused his opposite number of putting this curse on him as they both
        closed in on the Snitch.
